title: Fox Girls Presents | Forever We Roam | Holiday '13 Collectio
description:
The Fox crew traveled to Big Bear, California to capture the essence of this Holiday collection. We were hoping for snow, and to our advantage, a blizzard rolled in. Fox Girls Abby Brothers & Lauren Young toughed out the cold, had a blast & delivered one of our most beautiful seasons yet. 

Models: 
Abby Brothers
Lauren Young

Camera/Edit:
Ryan Marcus

Camera:
Veesh

Art Direction:
Elley norman

Music:
Auction for the Promise Club
"If"
One EP
